{"tid":1912583,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】日本7-11一盒口罩賣1200港元惹議　店家: 「屬實但無奈」","createTime":"2020-03-06T07:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T10:48:42.000Z","uid":226548,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"688735e7fe33377c159ae4b252d52fd99cb10a0f","tid":1912583,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e6113d86f91ff14194c064d.jpg/8CMYviXPuX1ia9zBBPUTg8brGlPaWKa5yr7PS8q-z0s?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e6113d86f91ff14194c064d.jpg%2F8CMYviXPuX1ia9zBBPUTg8brGlPaWKa5yr7PS8q-z0s%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=a27ec267&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019冠狀病毒病（COVID-19，俗稱武漢肺炎）疫情，日本口罩嚴重不足。日本一間7-11便利店被指以超高價出售口罩，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一盒60個口罩叫價1.69萬日圓（約1200港元）</span></strong>，因此惹來批評，日本7-11最後為事件致歉。<br />\n<br />\n日本網上流傳一張照片，上傳者聲稱在居所附近的一間7-11便利店正以超高價出售口罩，一盒60個的口罩售價達到約1200港元。在非疫情時期，同款口罩正常格價為一盒600日圓（約40港元），當地人不滿如今<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「炒價」達到約30倍</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>7-11為事件致歉</strong><br />\n<br />\n照片在網上廣泛流傳，日本7-11本部其後發表聲明，表示已要求該分店停止出售口罩，並指出原因是該店「為應大量顧客需求關係，在網上購買口罩後轉售」，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">因網上口罩均以炒價發售，所以售價才如此驚人</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n7-11聲明就事件致歉，並稱已要求店舖以合理價格出售口罩。"},{"pid":"9ba75c8a601aecd54376f9bb6dc772d4715b829b","tid":1912583,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e60c4dba5af56141f1d7fec.jpg/qFskSS9dUmEayl2v5W46iUnqC_nqz4heku0ZEZLtGRE?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e60c4dba5af56141f1d7fec.jpg%2FqFskSS9dUmEayl2v5W46iUnqC_nqz4heku0ZEZLtGRE%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=ed61c5eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網上有網民拍照，一盒60個普通防花粉和防塵的口罩，售價1.69萬日圓（Twitter圖片）"},{"pid":"f07650effdde2c769a9b4fd399afbc2085d5019f","tid":1912583,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:35:10.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/世界說/443870/新冠肺炎-日本7-11一盒口罩賣1200港元惹議-店家稱實屬無奈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E8%AA%AA%2F443870%2F%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC7-11%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%92%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E8%B3%A31200%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%83%E6%83%B9%E8%AD%B0-%E5%BA%97%E5%AE%B6%E7%A8%B1%E5%AF%A6%E5%B1%AC%E7%84%A1%E5%A5%88&d=%2FrzxgVsCSRBeEmt1flTkcMbSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=cc925279\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/世界說/443870/新冠肺炎-日本7-11一盒口罩賣1200港元惹議-店家稱實屬無奈</a>"},{"pid":"2940c4812280a2538f1a709831aa5c4de6c5a438","tid":1912583,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:41:31.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n合理價格即係無貨 唔會拎出黎賣<br />\n我放上網炒賣唔好？<br />\n商家佬點解要賤價賣？<br />\n食檬左？"},{"pid":"5595051033ee661cfa2156618fd6acee6003bc32","tid":1912583,"uid":22590,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T07:45:34.000Z","msg":"01垃圾標題 唔好寫到全線7-11都賣緊咁<br />\n<br />\n係有 <span style=\"color: red;\">一間</span> 7-11 個<span style=\"color: red;\">店東</span>獨自用炒價放係自己間舖度賣<br />\n當然問題係佢唔應該放係舖賣<br />\n要炒自己靜靜雞炒, 影衰7-11"},{"pid":"303dc6c4e9eba3e5f5eabe3357d9aff7f8aa7574","tid":1912583,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1af3489cc95cc17e052edccf1516da8a55a49ce6","tid":1912583,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:13:12.000Z","msg":"手寫price tag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244221acf36809e4dd3808d1dea09a66dca7728b","tid":1912583,"uid":196535,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T09:15:07.000Z","msg":"CLS 這是真的日本? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\